==English==

===Etymology===
From ''[[Nippon]]'', native name for Japan

===Verb===
{{en-verb|nipponiz|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To make or become [[Japanese]], as to customs, culture, or style.
# {{transitive}} to convert to [[katakana]] or to enable to work with the Japanese script.
# {{transitive}} to translate into Japanese.

